      "span_text": "For delivery, siRNAs for gene-targeting experiments have only been introduced into cells via classic gene-transfer methods, such as liposome-mediated transfection, electroporation and microinjection, which require the chemical or enzymatic synthesis of siRNAs [CITATION_1] ."
